013package org.apache.juneau.http.annotation;
014
015import static org.apache.juneau.common.internal.Utils.*;
016import static org.apache.juneau.internal.ArrayUtils.*;
017import static java.lang.annotation.ElementType.*;
018import static java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy.*;
019import java.lang.annotation.*;
020import org.apache.juneau.*;
021import org.apache.juneau.annotation.*;
022import org.apache.juneau.httppart.*;
023import org.apache.juneau.reflect.*;
024import org.apache.juneau.svl.*;
025
026/**
027 * Utility classes and methods for the {@link FormData @FormData} annotation.
028 *
029 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
030 * </ul>
031 */
032public class FormDataAnnotation {
033
034   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
035   // Static
036   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
037
038   /** Default value */
039   public static final FormData DEFAULT = create().build();
040
041   /**
042    * Instantiates a new builder for this class.
043    *
044    * @return A new builder object.
045    */
046   public static Builder create() {
047      return new Builder();
048   }
049
050   /**
051    * Instantiates a new builder for this class.
052    *
053    * @param on The targets this annotation applies to.
054    * @return A new builder object.
055    */
056   public static Builder create(Class<?>...on) {
057      return create().on(on);
058   }
059
060   /**
061    * Instantiates a new builder for this class.
062    *
063    * @param on The targets this annotation applies to.
064    * @return A new builder object.
065    */
066   public static Builder create(String...on) {
067      return create().on(on);
068   }
069
070   /**
071    * Returns <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
072    *
073    * @param a The annotation to check.
074    * @return <jk>true</jk> if the specified annotation contains all default values.
075    */
076   public static boolean empty(FormData a) {
077      return a == null || DEFAULT.equals(a);
078   }
079
080   /**
081    * Finds the name from the specified lists of annotations.
082    *
083    * <p>
084    * The last matching name found is returned.
085    *
086    * @param pi The parameter.
087    * @return The last matching name, or {@link Value#empty()} if not found.
088    */
089   public static Value<String> findName(ParamInfo pi) {
090      Value<String> n = Value.empty();
091      pi.forEachAnnotation(FormData.class, x -> isNotEmpty(x.value()), x -> n.set(x.value()));
092      pi.forEachAnnotation(FormData.class, x -> isNotEmpty(x.name()), x -> n.set(x.name()));
093      return n;
094   }
095
096   /**
097    * Finds the default value from the specified list of annotations.
098    *
099    * @param pi The parameter.
100    * @return The last matching default value, or {@link Value#empty()} if not found.
101    */
102   public static Value<String> findDef(ParamInfo pi) {
103      Value<String> n = Value.empty();
104      pi.forEachAnnotation(FormData.class, x -> isNotEmpty(x.def()), x -> n.set(x.def()));
105      return n;
106   }
107
108   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
109   // Builder
110   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
111
112   /**
113    * Builder class.
114    *
115    * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
116    *    <li class='jm'>{@link org.apache.juneau.BeanContext.Builder#annotations(Annotation...)}
117    * </ul>
118    */
119   public static class Builder extends TargetedAnnotationTMFBuilder<Builder> {
120
121      Class<? extends HttpPartParser> parser = HttpPartParser.Void.class;
122      Class<? extends HttpPartSerializer> serializer = HttpPartSerializer.Void.class;
123      Schema schema = SchemaAnnotation.DEFAULT;
124      String def="", name="", value="";
125
126      /**
127       * Constructor.
128       */
129      protected Builder() {
130         super(FormData.class);
131      }
132
133      /**
134       * Instantiates a new {@link FormData @FormData} object initialized with this builder.
135       *
136       * @return A new {@link FormData @FormData} object.
137       */
138      public FormData build() {
139         return new Impl(this);
140      }
141
142      /**
143       * Sets the {@link FormData#def} property on this annotation.
144       *
145       * @param value The new value for this property.
146       * @return This object.
147       */
148      public Builder def(String value) {
149         this.def = value;
150         return this;
151      }
152
153      /**
154       * Sets the {@link FormData#name} property on this annotation.
155       *
156       * @param value The new value for this property.
157       * @return This object.
158       */
159      public Builder name(String value) {
160         this.name = value;
161         return this;
162      }
163
164      /**
165       * Sets the {@link FormData#parser} property on this annotation.
166       *
167       * @param value The new value for this property.
168       * @return This object.
169       */
170      public Builder parser(Class<? extends HttpPartParser> value) {
171         this.parser = value;
172         return this;
173      }
174
175      /**
176       * Sets the {@link FormData#schema} property on this annotation.
177       *
178       * @param value The new value for this property.
179       * @return This object.
180       */
181      public Builder schema(Schema value) {
182         this.schema = value;
183         return this;
184      }
185
186      /**
187       * Sets the {@link FormData#serializer} property on this annotation.
188       *
189       * @param value The new value for this property.
190       * @return This object.
191       */
192      public Builder serializer(Class<? extends HttpPartSerializer> value) {
193         this.serializer = value;
194         return this;
195      }
196
197      /**
198       * Sets the {@link FormData#value} property on this annotation.
199       *
200       * @param value The new value for this property.
201       * @return This object.
202       */
203      public Builder value(String value) {
204         this.value = value;
205         return this;
206      }
207
208      // <FluentSetters>
209
210
211      // </FluentSetters>
212   }
213
214   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
215   // Implementation
216   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
217
218   private static class Impl extends TargetedAnnotationTImpl implements FormData {
219
220      private final Class<? extends HttpPartParser> parser;
221      private final Class<? extends HttpPartSerializer> serializer;
222      private final String name, value, def;
223      private final Schema schema;
224
225      Impl(Builder b) {
226         super(b);
227         this.def = b.def;
228         this.name = b.name;
229         this.parser = b.parser;
230         this.schema = b.schema;
231         this.serializer = b.serializer;
232         this.value = b.value;
233         postConstruct();
234      }
235
236      @Override /* FormData */
237      public String def() {
238         return def;
239      }
240
241      @Override /* FormData */
242      public String name() {
243         return name;
244      }
245
246      @Override /* FormData */
247      public Class<? extends HttpPartParser> parser() {
248         return parser;
249      }
250
251      @Override /* FormData */
252      public Schema schema() {
253         return schema;
254      }
255
256      @Override /* FormData */
257      public Class<? extends HttpPartSerializer> serializer() {
258         return serializer;
259      }
260
261      @Override
262      public String value() {
263         return value;
264      }
265   }
266
267   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
268   // Appliers
269   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
270
271   /**
272    * Applies targeted {@link FormData} annotations to a {@link org.apache.juneau.BeanContext.Builder}.
273    */
274   public static class Applier extends AnnotationApplier<FormData,BeanContext.Builder> {
275
276      /**
277       * Constructor.
278       *
279       * @param vr The resolver for resolving values in annotations.
280       */
281      public Applier(VarResolverSession vr) {
282         super(FormData.class, BeanContext.Builder.class, vr);
283      }
284
285      @Override
286      public void apply(AnnotationInfo<FormData> ai, BeanContext.Builder b) {
287         FormData a = ai.inner();
288         if (isEmptyArray(a.on(), a.onClass()))
289            return;
290         b.annotations(a);
291      }
292   }
293
294   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
295   // Other
296   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
297
298   /**
299    * A collection of {@link FormData @FormData annotations}.
300    */
301   @Documented
302   @Target({METHOD,TYPE})
303   @Retention(RUNTIME)
304   @Inherited
305   public static @interface Array {
306
307      /**
308       * The child annotations.
309       *
310       * @return The annotation value.
311       */
312      FormData[] value();
313   }
